OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSouthern Lebanon: BBC sees 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fair strike destruction in  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdeserted towns             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Spiralling tensions and cross-border   
OL,6, strikes which have killed more than 70 
OL,7, civilians in Lebanon have turned parts 
OL,8, of south into ghost towns. Residents   
OL,9, have fled, leaving their homes at risk 
OL,10, of destruction. The BBC went on patrol 
OL,11, with the UN's peacekeeping force there 
OL,12, to see what has happened.              
OL,14,FThe huge crater containing a mangled   
OL,15,Fmattress buried under a pile of dust   
OL,16,Fand stone is all that's left of the    
OL,17,Fbuilding that stood on this spot just  
OL,18,Fdays ago.                              
